History
Machinery Contractors was established in 1993

Profile
MC has its headquarters in Brits, Northwest Province;
Our management team is actively involved in the design, fabrication and marketing of our products and have over 20 years accumulative experience in the industry.
Staff complement of 61 full-time employees
22% of the staff were classified as professional and a further 17% as skilled. The skilled technical team was underpinned by an experienced labour force.;
